			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">$2005 and $2006 share an internal register inside the PPU. When you do updates through $2006/$2007, you overwrite this register. So after you update video memory, you need to set $2005 again before the next frame begins.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
