						<div class="postbody">Reference material for tepples' statements:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_scrolling">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_scrolling</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/The_skinny_on_NES_scrolling">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/The_ ... _scrolling</a><!-- m --><br /><br />The short version is: do your <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">lda #0 / sta $2005 / sta $2005</tt> after you do all of your $2006/$2007 updates, and before the start of the next frame (e.g. do all that within NMI).</div>

